```r
sinspuAlpha %>%
  left_join(.,viralPos) %>%
  filter(index %in% sinspu) -> ctcomp

summary(lmer(data = ctcomp,
             Shannon ~ ct + sampleloc + (ct * sampleloc) + (1|patientid)))

sinspuAlpha %>%
  left_join(.,viralPos) %>%
  filter(index %in% sinspu) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = Shannon,
             y = ct)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth(method = \lm\") +
